    <div class="pk-about__mission">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>Pankui is a brand that offers a wide range of high-quality, innovative and beautifully crafted products for everyday use. We believe in making our products accessible and convenient for every Indian kitchen &mdash; so you can cook, store and live with quiet calm.</p>
